It is very simple to install webservers on http.

Steps to update and install the required packages to install nginx on http:
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install nginx
sudo service nginx start
sudo service nginx stop
sudo service nginx restart

Steps to update and install the required packages to install apache2 on http:
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install apache2
sudo service apache2 start
sudo service apache2 stop
sudo service apache2 restart

